'''Alberto Stevens''' is a judge who presided over the case of [[Harold Allen]].

==History==
When [[Harold Allen]] was sued for malpractice over the death of Martin Weiser, Alberto presided over the hearing.

==Career==
He is a judge.

==Notes and Trivia==
*He was credited as Judge.
